'''Landslasher-1''' was one of four floating cities called [[Landslasher]]s located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Peekoine]]. It, along with [[Landslasher-2]] and [[Landslasher-3|3]], maintained the current canals of the planet, while [[Landslasher-4]] carved out new ones.

